Senate President, Bukola Saraki has declared to run for president under the platform of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP). Saraki made the declaration on Thursday at the National dialogue conference organised by the #NotTooYoungToRun Movement, in the presence of the PDP National Chairman, Prince Uche Secondus in Abuja. His full speech below: My brothers, My sisters, Let’s Grow Nigeria Together. God bless you all.  